<p>
<b>What is Pratilipi ?</b>
<br/>
We believe in the age old adage that "you become what you read". Owing to this philosophy we want to read good content, without any barriers. Pratilipi is a platform to encourage that. We want us to be able to discover, read and share our favourite content in any language, device and format of our choice. For more details read our <a href="/about">About</a> page.
</p>

<p>
<b>Who are the people behind Pratilipi ?</b>
<br/>
We are five young Indians who are all united by our love for great content and awesome chai. If you love either of these things come and say '<a href="/about#team">Hi</a>'
</p>

<p>
